name: testOpenDefaultBuildPopUpOfMultiConfiguration
description: Verify that default build bubble to MultiConfiguration project is present on Time line on Build History page
descriptionHtml: Verify that default build bubble to MultiConfiguration project is present on Time line on Build History page

testStage.description: Verify that default build bubble to MultiConfiguration project is present on Time line on Build History page

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' on the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click 'Build History' on the side menu
Click last default build bubble on the Timeline
Verify that default build bubble pop up has default from header text
